            <title>Video S5. Animated neuron pictograph from alternative splicing score of cortical neurons, related to Figure 3</title>
            <p>The video is created from the E14.5 stage to the 21st month. Color shades of cellular compartments and organelles are based on the enrichment of genes with high alternative splicing score (Ψ &gt; 0.9) from Weyn-Vanhentenryck et al., 2018<sup>5</sup></p>
          </caption>
