      <p id="p0170">Overall, these and additional examples with applications of <italic>expressyouRcell</italic> (<xref rid="mmc1" ref-type="supplementary-material">Figures S1</xref>–<xref rid="mmc1" ref-type="supplementary-material">S3</xref>, and, <xref rid="mmc2" ref-type="supplementary-material">Video S1. Animated neuron pictograph from TRAP-seq of cortical neurons - downregulated genes, related to Figure 2</xref>, <xref rid="mmc3" ref-type="supplementary-material">Video S2. Animated neuron pictograph from TRAP-seq of cortical neurons - upregulated genes, related to Figure 2</xref>, <xref rid="mmc4" ref-type="supplementary-material">Video S3. Animated neuron pictograph from TRAP-seq of cortical neurons - downregulated genes, related to Figure 2</xref>, <xref rid="mmc5" ref-type="supplementary-material">Video S4. Animated neuron pictograph from TRAP-seq of cortical neurons - upregulated genes, related to Figure 2</xref>, <xref rid="mmc6" ref-type="supplementary-material">Video S5. Animated neuron pictograph from alternative splicing score of cortical neurons, related to Figure 3</xref>, <xref rid="mmc7" ref-type="supplementary-material">Video S6. Animated cell pictograph from protein abundance levels of hiPSCs, related to Figure 4</xref>, <xref rid="mmc8" ref-type="supplementary-material">Video S7. Animated cell pictographs from scRNA-seq of neurons. The Video is created from day 9.5 to day 13.5, related to Figure 7fig7</xref>, <xref rid="mmc9" ref-type="supplementary-material">Video S8. Animated microglia pictograph from RNA-seq of microglial cells - downregulated genes, related to Table 1</xref>, <xref rid="mmc10" ref-type="supplementary-material">Video S9. Animated microglia pictograph from RNA-seq of microglial cells - upregulated genes, related to Table 1</xref>, <xref rid="mmc11" ref-type="supplementary-material">Video S10. Animated microglia pictograph from RNA-seq of microglial cells - downregulated genes, related to Table 1</xref>, <xref rid="mmc12" ref-